00117 void CHPQuantificationData::GetQuantificationEntry(int index, affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationData &entry)
00118 {
00119         OpenQuantificationDataSet();
00120         if (entries && entries->IsOpen())
00121         {
00122         entry.id = -1;
00123         entry.name.clear();
00124                 if (firstColumnType == ASCIICharColType)
00125                         entries->GetData(index, 0, entry.name);
00126                 else if (firstColumnType == UnicodeCharColType)
00127                 {
00128             std::wstring wprobeSetName;
00129             entries->GetData(index, 0, wprobeSetName);
00130             entry.name = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(wprobeSetName);
00131                 }
00132         else if (firstColumnType == IntColType)
00133             entries->GetData(index, 0, entry.id);
00134         entries->GetData(index, 1, entry.quantification);
00135         }
00136 }

00190 ParameterNameValueTypeList CHPQuantificationData::GetAlgParams()
00191 {
00192         ParameterNameValueTypeList nvt;
00193         ParameterNameValueTypeIt begin, end;
00194         ParameterNameValueType param;
00195 
00196         genericData.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->GetNameValIterators(begin, end);
00197         while(begin != end)
00198         {
00199                 std::wstring key = begin->GetName();
00200                 if(key.compare(0, ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S.size(),ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S) == 0)
00201                 {
00202                         param = *begin;
00203                         key.erase(0, ALGORITHM_PARAM_NAME_PREFIX_S.size());
00204                         param.SetName(key);
00205                         nvt.push_back(param);
00206                 }
00207                 begin++;
00208         }
00209         return nvt;
00210 }
